 help fails, God will never forsake thee.', 2878, 0), (340740, 'Easy does it, boys. I just need help standing, not flying.', 142, 0), (340741, 'We need you to help us figure out how you can help us.', 182, 0), (340742, '[O]ur English divines are sounder in it than any in the world, generally: I think because they are more practical, and have had more wounded, tender consciences under cure, and less empty speculation and dispute (336-7).', 11465, 0), (340743, 'Monk is helper who to help us in spiritual way.', 4605, 0), (340744, 'The road out there is long, to find the right people is like to find the people which will show how much times you have been right. All people remember when you screw up, but few remember when you are doing the stuff right,... the only thing which can help you is the quotes - so keep reading them!', 4605, 0), (340745, 'The entire room turns and stares. There’s no doubt what they see—ripped jeans, a black T-shirt, tattoos and earrings. I don’t care what they see. All I care about is what she sees: a person unwelcomed or the guy she ', 345, 0), (340746, 'I don''t want to see him alone. He says things that annoy me. He gives me good advice.', 40, 0), (340747, 'Solutions, not problems; they''re in there somewhere.', 55557, 0), (340748, 'We were trying to write this song about how to help somebody – almost like a manual, or like a formula of what you do when somebody you love is in trouble – and we just couldn’t do it. So what was left was sorta this shell or outline around the missing answer. As I sang a couple takes of it, everything just hit me of how helpless we are to handle the pressures of life – to handle the cards that are dealt to us and the people close to us. And I remember, like, breaking down.', 55558, 0), (340749, 'Some books don''t answer the inside, I read one comic called Ms.Marvel!Under Marvel can be understand that this person is powerful and can handle a lot of stuff, but reality this wasn''t a powerful one or one strong. This