, 0), (340966, 'Always remember that the tales of another are never as wondrous as your own.', 1584, 0), (340967, 'Once in a very blue moon, John Tallow imagined his younger self standing down the timeline of his present life, bare toes curling in teenage beach sand, looking ahead to today and watching his future life collapse in on itself like a dying star. His future life becoming small and dark and dense, its gravity apparently grim and inescapable.Once in a very blue moon, John Tallow spent some cash on a bottle of vodka and drank it at home within an hour.', 1871, 0), (340968, 'Success, as we categorize it, is a simple and pitiable thing. It''s only a matter of degree of wanting, and accident. Wanting plays the major role in everybody''s life--accident all the others. The only condition any of us can be sure of in this universe is wanting. How tepid or burning hot the want is depends on accident. But since accident isn''t really as accidental as we''d like to think--accident is the great fooler and comforter of mankind--we become ''successful'' exactly to the degree we want.', 18847, 0), (340969, 'Life,perhaps less a document than an impression,conveyed through partial glances,stream-of-consciousness juxtapositions,unpredictable rhythms, a collage of sound,a conscientious diarist,a career of blackmail and scandal culminated in murder,a blind man with a will of iron and a nervous system of gossamer.', 30138, 0), (340970, 'Everything that has ever happened to me is still all with me.', 15511, 0), (340971, 'Don''t even listen to No body including your friends who tells you to Move On in life.  They often will have destroyed your Motivation causing an unexpected anxiety, and a severe brain stress until you give up. No matter how dead serious they are in order for you to understand them, reject their Anti-statement with the Power of your Assertion. They will foolishly halter your situation you had been encountering over the past year, when it all started from the beginning.Therefore, you MUST KEEP MOVING FORWARD.DO WHAT YOU NEED TO DO THAT NEEDS TO BE DONE.That is the way of succeeding in life in order to prove to everyone you''ve overcome the Obstacles and your Anxiety.', 20648, 0), (340972, 'A determined soul can never be defeated in life.', 2878, 0), (340973, 'Life is calmness with squabbling, accumulating traditions and self-consciousness. elaborate meals, medicine, law,pretty pictures unspoiled,rocking the cradle and holding the hammer, impressive skies of gray and blue, believing in what we can’t settle, the mystery of iniquity,the absolutely sincere predictions of fools,lighter moods like these.', 30138, 0), (340974, 'It’s not so much about the cards you’re dealt; it’s a whole lot more about whether you play them well, or play them at all.', 4397, 0), (340975, 'Transforming Moment" yes I got it. I Committed. I Tried. I Executed. I Failed. I Motivated. I Succeed.', 12584, 0), (340976, 'This world today makes one by the day a recluse', 44532, 0), (340977, 'An element of wisdom is knowing that life experiences are blood brothers with climate change, whether you have the resources to detect weather changes, it can still surprise you anytime.', 9273, 0), (340978, 'If you let all the bad thing in life stop you', 55589, 0), (340979, 'And you thought there was only one exit door...', 3612, 0), (340980, 'We live individual lives with the consciousness of death and awareness of the past. But the most important part of that sentence is the individual part. Let yourself be humbled by the experiences people have been having for thousands of years. And speak of it.', 55590, 0), (340981, 'Careful how you judge others', 55591, 0), (340982, 'Thinking to do or not to do is not the right thing to do,just think the right way and do it', 23355, 0), (340983, 'i''m wiz a girl,i call her name 10 times before you breathe once ,it''s not majic,it''s not logic ,it''s just a love!', 55592, 0), (340984, 'That’s the way life is sometimes: you can fix things up, but you can’t make them all better.', 2735, 0), (340985, 'Learnings from any training you have attended will not make any sense if you are not applying it, make sense .', 5602, 0), (340986, 'time never heals everything in life,but memories do', 55593, 0), (340987, 'Life is full of risks.It is matter to take risks than doing nothing.Dare to take risks in life.', 27144, 0), (340988, 'Three, two, one, and f*ck it!', 55594, 0), (340989, 'I''m not going to drown in what I can''t change.', 1376, 0), (340990, 'In every moments of life, we''re all having up and down.If there are no up or down, it means we didn''t have any life.', 31534, 0), (340991, 'The words marriage and divorce were always used together, like they went hand in hand together.', 27, 0), (340992, 'An important memory is like a gravitational field--the mind is compelled to return to it again and again. It is like a moon', 55595, 0), (340993, 'Nothing is worth having if it isn''t worth showing off…', 52797, 0), (340994, 'The world has never favored the experimental life. It despises poets, fanatics, prophets and lovers.', 4976, 0), (340995, 'you are only what you are when no one is watching.', 55596, 0), (340996, 'However far back you go you will find all experiences linked by slender threads.', 10455, 0), (340997, 'Life is an experience and this experience is to gain a life', 50157, 0), (340998, 'You''ll never know what you''re capable of if you never take the first step and try.', 54049, 0), (340999, 'Know the adjectives that define you and pay no heed to the verbs that defy you.', 55597, 0), (341000, 'The only true wisdome is knowing you know nothing.', 55598, 0);
